    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You sheathe yourself with thunder and lightning, letting it form a protective shield over your body. You gain a +2 deflection bonus to Defense, and electricity resistance 5. If a creature hits you with an unarmed or melee attack, it takes 1d4 electric damage (CR applies). In addition, you gain a +4 bonus to saves against Electric effects, and if such an effect allows a Reflex save for half damage, you take no damage on a successful save instead.</p>\n\n\n\n",
